# Project 4: Business Data Chat Agent

## Overview
An intelligent agent that allows users to ask natural language questions about structured business data (sales data in this case) and get accurate answers by converting questions into pandas code.

## Features
- Natural language to pandas code conversion
- Accurate data analysis and insights
- Interactive Gradio interface
- Powered by Groq LLM + Pandas Agent
- Handles complex queries (grouping, filtering, aggregations)

## Tech Stack
- Pandas
- LangChain Experimental (Pandas Agent)
- Groq (LLM)
- Gradio (UI)

## How It Works
1. User asks a question in natural language
2. The agent generates and executes pandas code
3. Returns accurate results with reasoning

## Example Questions & Answers
- "What is the total sales?" → $510,000
- "Which region has the highest sales?" → West ($125,000)
- "What is the best performing product?" → Monitor

## Key Learnings
- How to build LLM-powered data analysis agents
- Converting natural language to executable code
- Building interactive data tools with Gradio
- Working with structured business data

## Future Improvements
- Support for uploading custom CSV files
- Add visualization (charts)
- Support for SQL databases
- Multi-turn conversation memory

